Release Update: Experience Faster Salesforce CRM Connector Refreshes

Refresh a Streaming Data Transform

When you update a streaming data transform, you can now apply the changes to all your data—current and incoming—by rebuilding the target data lake object.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This feature is available starting in June 2024.

How: From Recently Viewed, click next to the data transform, and select Rebuild.
title: Refresh a Streaming Data Transform in Salesforce
